listing.name: Modern apartment close to centre
listing.description:
A cozy renovated apartment with balcony. Close to 2 parks, museums and much more.  At small square at back side of building, very quiet. Only 8 minuts  from tram and metro, 12 minutes from Central  Station. Booming neighbourhood.

8 minutes walking from metro and tram station. Central Station 12 minutes by metro. Close to Schiphol airport as well.
listing.house_rules:
I love my apartment  and like to share this feeling with others. 
So please avond noise  at the balcony  and in the apartment after 10 pm.
No pets allowed.
Smoking is allowed on the balcony.

photos.caption: Boxspring bed for 2 persons. Bedroom has high walls and a large window. Because the apartment is located at the back side of the building you will have a good night sleep.
I will make some space for you in this clothes chest, standing in the bedroom.

review.comments:
Pauline is an amazing and accommodating host. She welcomed and helped us with our luggage upon arrival and then talked us through the facilities in the flat. The flat is clean and really cute. The little balcony is a bonus! Location is fab as only four stops away from Central station and bus/ tram stops also nearby. The area is up-and-coming and has a few cafes, bike shops and supermarket within walking distance. 

Overall we had an amazing experience - thanks a lot, Pauline, would definitely love to come back :)
